query:
UPDATE persoane_fizice 
        SET 
            tip = $2,
            cnp_hash = $3,
            nume = $4,
            prenume = $5,
            serie_act_identitate = $6,
            numar_act_identitate = $7,
            data_nasterii = $8,
            cetatenie = $9,
            dovada_drept_folosinta = $10,
            cod_caen = $11,
            data_inregistrarii = $12,
            euid = $13,
            nr_ordine_reg_comert = $14,
            platitor_tva = $15,
            stare_fiscala = $16,
            inregistrat_in_spv = $17,
            updated_at = NOW()
        WHERE uuid = $1
